{"tid":256073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聯和墟逸峯商場入口道大門真係世界級","createTime":"2017-05-24T09:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T10:08:27.000Z","uid":91427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a30f116011b14b655b4deaa8cc8b230901f5ab6","tid":256073,"uid":91427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:25:40.000Z","msg":"真係世界級咁難開<br />\n<br />\n第一次去呢個商場<br />\n已經發覺道門好難開<br />\n我推道門發覺無反應<br />\n仲以為道門lock左<br />\n搞到我係門口呆左2秒<br />\n最後我紮起馬步，用齊兩隻手先推開道門<br />\n個一刻我以為自已係西西弗斯係度推緊石<br />\n都未完，原來大門係兩層設計<br />\n出面開完入面係仲要開多道<br />\n<br />\n而且佢兩道門寫住&quot;拉&quot;<br />\n其實第一道係可以推<br />\n我推左第一道<br />\n所以第二道我瀨左野<br />\n<br />\n今日，我重返逸峯商場<br />\n不過今次我係有備而黎<br />\n雙手開門太柒<br />\n所以今次我用單手開<br />\n而且有少少技巧<br />\n唔好用死力，要用陰力<br />\n兩道門一推一拉<br />\n過程一氣呵成，簡直完美<br />\n<br />\n不過開門既時候投入左少少<br />\n好似呵屎咁&quot;唔～&quot;左一聲<br />\n隔離個師奶望住我<br />\n我知道佢唔係恥笑我<br />\n而係賦予我認同既眼神<br />\n<br />\n離開商場既時候，已經係黃昏<br />\n仲落緊陣陣細雨<br />\n我回頭望逸峯最後一眼<br />\n心中萬分感慨<br />\n我發現<br />\n左手邊有道自動門<br />\n<br />\nanyway，佢道門真係好難開"},{"pid":"c37beeb0893ff8a676d5dc31b0cea6a7cbd4a935","tid":256073,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒"},{"pid":"a302d48ba9731769e92899ed4baa72e89135d040","tid":256073,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"bede9d6e735b0d3c01d4817489d6d25b3df8265e","tid":256073,"uid":1314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"對門嘅難開程度同你個戇鳩程度一樣"},{"pid":"42cd5a3b895186b399b4d908414032fa742d2386","tid":256073,"uid":91427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對門嘅難開程度同你個戇鳩程度一樣</blockquote><br />\n對門難開D"},{"pid":"9561ccc79596a72b14ddf62eb674b916db8eca47","tid":256073,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:56:46.000Z","msg":"推門都無力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d25e3b6995f3cb0d51ec3eb378cead9b1f78dd","tid":256073,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會係你潺咗啲"},{"pid":"cc9bc9235c7e1573627d9a25ea13cb8bdea2ff7c","tid":256073,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"吹水啦，依家有道自動門架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2c760a120b3c7f29ed8fc7e86b2dc2342e948b","tid":256073,"uid":91427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推門都無力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你過黎推下就知<br />\n比一般既門係難開好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d88acf145f84f08f0e912d5fce28e08755dc6b8","tid":256073,"uid":91427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吹水啦，依家有道自動門架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n道門依然難開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d15545d55b74811746cd1efce5098f74cbb7fc","tid":256073,"uid":91427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係你潺咗啲</blockquote><br />\n門難開＋我潺"}]}